{"tid":1338913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦發表聲明譴責示威者","createTime":"2019-07-21T14:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:01:10.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f02c7542872c11feb69f48b1835f790fcd9ae300","tid":1338913,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"中聯辦發表聲明，對部分激進示威者圍堵中聯辦大樓，並污損國徽的行為表示嚴厲譴責。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦負責人表示，在今日的遊行隊伍到達終點後，部分激進示威者圍堵中聯辦，破壞設施，污損國徽，噴塗侮辱國家、民族的字句，這些行徑已經完全超出了和平示威的範疇，不僅違反《基本法》和香港本地法律，更嚴重挑戰「一國兩制」的底線，嚴重挑戰中央權威，對此表示最強烈的憤慨和譴責，並堅決支持特區政府和警隊依法嚴懲違法暴力行為，維護香港的社會穩定。<br />\n<br />\n該負責人強調，中央駐港機構嚴格按照憲法、《基本法》和中央授權在港履行職責，不容挑戰。他呼籲香港社會全體市民認清極少數激進分子的暴力危害和本質，堅決維護「一國兩制」，維護法治。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2196653/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2196653%2F&d=7LXG2TbyL57SoPLQ%2FF4DpRZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=275650f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2196653/</a>"},{"pid":"d575c51a9ee6b5ff7b9945c90d47722091c379f3","tid":1338913,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126d0b835fde1b5be42639720f95a5acdcbd2a26","tid":1338913,"uid":2419,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141002/large/a0201a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141002%2Flarge%2Fa0201a.gif&h=e4551583&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b7a0126bca81b34d2eec252732f9bd2f714d70f","tid":1338913,"uid":95520,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"嚇得我啊<br />\n譴責咋吓話"},{"pid":"e7ac35a1b7c86185e2ef391057b055d4ac2130d6","tid":1338913,"uid":54303,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"c